<!-- ============= WHY DO WE FEEL TIRED ============= -->
<section class="s symptoms-bg">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="s-head center">
      <span class="rv-marker">The drain · 01</span>
      <span class="s-eyebrow" style="display:none">Why do we feel tired</span>
      <h2 class="s-title">Energy is not just <em>about sleep</em>.</h2>
      <p class="s-sub">Modern life constantly demands energy, focus and stamina — yet several daily factors quietly drain you long before bedtime catches up.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="symptoms-figure">
